| (2.5) |  | \frac{1}{1+\Gamma(1-\beta)s}\leq E\_{\beta}(-s)\leq\frac{1}{1+\frac{s}{\Gamma(1% +\beta)}},\quad s\geq 0. |  |

For more details about the Mittag-Leffler function and its properties, see [26, 32].

